

To run:
Start up.
Get a box and an area.
Center the box in the screen's box.
Draw and fill the box with the green pen.
Convert the area to square inches.
Write the area then " square inches" below the box.
Refresh the screen.
Wait for the escape key.

To get a box and an area:
Make the box 4 inches by 2 inches.
Put the box's area into the area.

To center a box in the screen's box:
Start in the center of the screen's box.